    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anno Deo propitio pontificatus
                        domini nostri <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1591">Benedicti</persName>
                        summi pontificis et universalis <rs key="#Popes">pape</rs> in apostolica
                        sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede anno quarto sitque imperante
                        domnus <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/261">Chonradus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> in Italia anno nono, die tertio mensis
                        iulii, indictione quarta, in loco qui dicitur
                        <placeName>Sablone</placeName>. Petimus a te <persName
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities"><name ref="Albericus/Turco"
                                >Alberico qui vocatur Tussco</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">misso</rs> dominus <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1574">Guido</persName> religiosus <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposea</placeName></orgName> uti nobis
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martinus</name></persName> filius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gorzius">Gorzio</name></persName> tam per me
                        quam per personam de <persName><name ref="Eilvitefredus"
                            >Eilvitefredi</name></persName> et consortibus meis seu filiis et
                        heredibus nostris <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellario
                            nomine</rs> concedisti nobis de re iuris nominati monasterii, idest
                        concedisti nobis medietate in integram de omnes <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sex sortes et portiones</rs> integra vel
                        quantamcunque abes et detines <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Magrus"
                                >Magri</name></persName> filio infra ... <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Forests #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Wine #Pigs #Hay/fodder #Levies #Fruits/vegetables #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2427"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Forests #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Wine #Pigs #Hay/fodder #Levies #Fruits/vegetables #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#places/3531">Lovignano</placeName></geogName> et in fundo qui
                        vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Forests #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Wine #Pigs #Hay/fodder #Levies #Fruits/vegetables #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2034"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Forests #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Wine #Pigs #Hay/fodder #Levies #Fruits/vegetables #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#places/4647">Punzano</placeName></geogName> et in fundo qui
                        vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Forests #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Wine #Pigs #Hay/fodder #Levies #Fruits/vegetables #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/1402"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Forests #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Wine #Pigs #Levies #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#places/4648">Vicoramerio</placeName></geogName> per singulis
                        locis ... <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, <rs>arbustis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs> per singulis locis; hec quia
                        concedisti nobis abendum, tenendum, possidendum, roncandum, pastinandum,
                        propaginandum, defensandum et in omnibus meliorandum, in annis advenientibus
                        viginti et novem ad renovandum ... petitione renovemur. Ita sane ut
                        inferramus <rs key="#Levies">terratico</rs> dare debeamus de singulis inibi
                        Dominus condonare dignatus est, oc est terratico: de <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs>, de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >sicale</rs> in campo capa quarta ... in area modio quarto, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">farre</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >ordeo</rs> in campo ... <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> manna octava, omnia
                            <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">minuto</rs> in area modio sesto, <rs
                            key="#Wine">vino</rs> anfora quarta, semel vice arbore pecto ponendo,
                        postea si vobis cessum; quod si glande habuerimus ... <rs key="#Pigs"
                            >porci</rs> ... dare debeamus porco uno; et si vinea pastinaverimus post
                        incolome ... fruere debeamus annos quinque; si ronco roncaverimus, fruere
                        debeamus annos quatuor; deductum ipsos ... colunico usque ad ripa <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4196">Pado</placeName> ad nave domnicam ubi
                        potuerit pervenire ad tollendum. Et non habeamus licentiam dandi, vendendi
                        ... commutare nos ... predicti petitoris sicut supra legitur; et non
                        habeamus licentiam de ipsa re ad nullo placito publico apulare nisi ad ...
                        et non ... Maiore quidem domnico vestro vel vestra dominacio et cum onore et
                        obbedientia susipere debeamus sine dolo vel fraude. Si quis vero pars
                        nostrum contra anc petitione ire tentaverimus et omnia sicut supra legitur
                        non observaverimus, det pars partis fidem servanti ante omnes litis initium
                        seu interpellatione pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri huntias duas</rs> et
                        post pene soluta manente anc petitione in suo robore et firmitate. Quas vero
                        petitione eo scripto Leo tabellio scribendam rogavit et unus alterius nobis
                        pariter iubemus, quod consecuti sumus, agamus Deum et vobis massima gratias,
                        sub die, mense et indictione quarta, in Sablone. Signum manus meas petitoris
                        ad omnia supradicta cui relectum est.</ab>
                </div>
